As someone who's been expressing outrage over the whole thing and am perfectly fine with people giving anyone guilty of harassment a good kick in the ass (metaphorically, not literally) I am fine with saying that I do not think EDHREC is a place to really speak on these kind of current events. It's also not Commander/EDH specific... It's bigger than any one format and kind of feels outside of our jurisdiction to really even get into.
I won't fire anyone who gets into fights with alt right incels on Twitter or Reddit outside of their capacity as an EDHREC writer even if a bunch not those alt right people email me and demand it
I have your back, but I don't think we drag this site into it.
There’s also plenty of big voices like the prof, wedge, jimmy and josh, Phil etc getting involved
